<p><span class="anchor" id="p20"></span>فَلَا يَكْفِي تغييب مَا دونهَا أَو تغييبها بدبر<a href="#p20" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p21"></span>وَلَا مُطَالبَة<a href="#p21" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p22"></span>للزَّوْج بالفيئة<a href="#p22" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p23"></span>إِن كَانَ بهَا<a href="#p23" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p24"></span>أَي الزَّوْجَة<a href="#p24" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
